{"type":"message","id":"b6e5404c","parentId":"393076f9","timestamp":"2026-04-12T07:25:10.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好，我在。  \n如果你是找主控这边，和 OpenClaw / agent / 机器人 / skill / 绑定 / 路由 / 配置 / 自动化有关的事，可以直接说。  \n比如你可以这样开头：\n\n- 主控：帮我看下机器人配置\n- 主控：这个 skill 为什么没生效\n- 主控：怎么做多 Agent 协同\n- 主控：帮我排查绑定/路由问题\n\n如果只是打个招呼，也可以——你好呀。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4d7453a01613920169db48c9df8881919be8c63cb241dd6a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":880,"output":123,"cacheRead":22912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23915,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775978692846,"responseId":"resp_0c4d7453a01613920169db48c73d5481918db9b3a05fbdec1a"}}
